UI generation complete for Ortavox Content Creation Assistant.

File written: app/page.tsx

Features implemented:
- Dashboard view with quick action cards, stats, and workflow overview
- Topic Research view with agent integration (TOPIC_RESEARCH agent)
- Content Generation view with tabbed results: Blog Post, Social Media (LinkedIn, X/Twitter, Facebook, Instagram), SEO
- Draft Editor view with quality scoring, changes list, suggestions, and brand voice alignment
- Publishing view with Notion + Google Calendar tool parameter forms
- Left sidebar navigation with icon tooltips
- Right sidebar with agent status panel and workflow progress tracker
- Sample Data toggle in top bar
- Cross-view state management (topics flow to content, content flows to editor, editor flows to publisher)
- Markdown rendering for all long-form content
- Inline error handling with retry capability
- Loading spinners with descriptive text
- Copy-to-clipboard functionality on all content sections
- Full Array.isArray() and optional chaining guards on all response data
- ErrorBoundary wrapping all page content
- Dark theme with violet/purple Ortavox branding
